items.sentence: Tell me I'm not the only one who saw this coming.
You'd better get out of here as soon as possible.
I spent a long time thinking about what Tom said.
Tom didn't open the letter that he got from Mary.
Tom is going to figure how to do that eventually.
I'm so sorry I didn't do what you asked me to do.
I'm so sorry I wasn't able to help you yesterday.
I'm so sorry I wasn't able to lend you any money.
Tom's cellphone started to vibrate in his pocket.
Tom and Mary started spending more time together.
